Foreign experts select Chile to combat Hanta[virus 27 Mar 2001;
Diagnosis of hantavirus infection in Representative Letelier still not
discarded (26 Mar);
2 new cases of hantavirus confirmed in Biobio province (23 Mar 2001);
Measures to prevent spread of hantavirus criticized (19 Mar 2001);
New case of hantavirus in 10th Regionn (19 Mar 2001);
Case of hantavirus confirmed in Bio Bio Region (16 Mar 2001);
MOH confirms 2 new cases of hantavirus (14 Mar 2001);
Illapel takes measures against the threat of hantavirus (13 Mar 2001).
In el diario El Mercurio:
